Class JSONSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.protheos.graph.JSONSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.graphstream.stream.AttributeSink, org.graphstream.stream.ElementSink, org.graphstream.stream.Sink

    public class JSONSender
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.graphstream.stream.Sink
    This class is responsible to send GraphStream event in JSON format to Gephi server, so as to communicate from GraphStream to Gephi.

    wumalbert
